Dialogue: 1,0:00:05.02,0:00:07.49,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(40,0)}{\c&HA0A0A0&}This story is fiction. The names of people,\Nplaces and groups are imaginary.\NObey traffic rules and drive safely.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:14.27,0:00:16.50,MainStyle,,0100,0000,0310,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord0}INITIAL
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.68,0:00:38.35,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Kogoeta machi ni giniro shita kemuri}Silver smoke in a freezing city...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.35,0:00:42.05,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{misugita yume no daisyou}...that's the cost of having an unachievable dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.05,0:00:45.78,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Kogoeta karada furikirenai omoi}A frozen body and unforgettable desire...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.78,0:00:49.45,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{accel funde gomakasu}You deceive yourself by stepping\Non the accelerator.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.45,0:00:56.81,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Yoru ni kowareta mama shisen tsuyoku togarasete}Although depressed in the night,\Nyour eyes are kept sharply open.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.81,0:01:04.20,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Dareno kimagure kara sekai sae mo owarisoude}You feel like someone's careless\Nact could end the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.20,0:01:06.15,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,"Break in 2 the nite" It's that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.15,0:01:09.73,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Obieta me wo shite lost in the night}Lost in the night with frightened eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.73,0:01:13.39,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{ochiteku yume ni dakareru}Embraced by a ruined dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.39,0:01:17.15,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Kodoku ga kowakute missin' my heart}Scared of loneliness, I'm missing you in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.15,0:01:20.86,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{jibun sae mo kizu tsukete}I almost hurt myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.86,0:01:24.54,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Taoreru kurai ni love me so much}Love me so much and knock me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.54,0:01:28.23,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{subete wo suttee anata wo}If only I can give up everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.23,0:01:31.89,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Ai suru koto sae dekitara}...and love you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.89,0:01:36.13,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{kitto sunao ni naresou}...I can be my true self.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.41,0:01:39.90,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi, this is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.90,0:01:41.37,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Who from?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.37,0:01:43.46,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,From Takahashi Ryosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.90,0:01:47.75,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.75,0:01:48.59,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...Ryosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.09,0:01:51.93,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}He's fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.93,0:01:53.90,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Although he lowered his power...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.67,0:01:57.84,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}...his exit speed is definitely faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.84,0:02:01.19,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}He won't lose.\NNo way he will!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.07,0:02:03.61,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,"Battle?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.46,0:02:06.64,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to fight someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.64,0:02:10.88,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,No.  We just call a car race a "battle."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.88,0:02:13.32,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't like it,\Nwhy don't you ignore him?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.82,0:02:16.48,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that I don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.48,0:02:20.76,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to run away, although\NI don't know if I can win.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.53,0:02:23.91,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you still think Takumi will lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.91,0:02:24.93,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.93,0:02:29.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if Takumi's a genius,\Nhe's only a high school kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.54,0:02:34.08,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how long he can keep up with\NTakahashi Ryosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.61,0:02:38.64,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I only have one reason for thinking\Nthat he might be able to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.28,0:02:43.04,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Takumi is Bunta's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.04,0:02:45.57,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}That crazy Bunta.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.90,0:02:53.60,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Keisuke, I've been thinking\Nabout this for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.60,0:02:56.58,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If I lose on the street...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.58,0:02:58.00,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll retire.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.16,0:03:00.65,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I've said that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.65,0:03:06.20,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...I can say that I've met two drivers\Nwho might defeat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.20,0:03:09.79,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,One of them is you, Keisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.79,0:03:11.13,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.13,0:03:13.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,And the other is...
Dialogue: 1,0:03:35.70,0:03:41.58,MainStyle,,0000,0050,0356,,{\fade(255,0,245,0,1010,4830,5820)}{\2a&HFF&}Last Great Battle
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.89,0:03:54.53,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.28,0:03:57.67,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.67,0:03:59.81,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck, Takumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.81,0:04:03.33,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I... I believe\Nthat you'll win!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.33,0:04:07.28,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,So outrun Takahashi Ryosuke and become\Nthe greatest star in Gunma!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.28,0:04:08.72,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.12,0:04:10.65,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.65,0:04:14.40,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Itsuki, he understands,\Nso leave him alone. {Good luck, Takumi}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.40,0:04:15.52,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.24,0:04:21.47,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just before 10 o'clock.\NYou're as laidback as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.12,0:04:25.53,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.87,0:04:57.64,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how someone as young\Nas you learned all these techniques...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.64,0:04:59.90,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...but you impress me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.90,0:05:06.41,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I've driven Akina's mountain passes more than\Nanyone else, so I'm familiar with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.41,0:05:09.83,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't use any special techniques.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.21,0:05:16.64,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You must've misunderstood,\Nand think too highly of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.30,0:05:20.78,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That's interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.78,0:05:25.63,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you don't know\Nmuch about yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.71,0:05:33.75,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You're interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.02,0:05:37.30,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to spend more time\Ntalking to you someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.81,0:05:44.30,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.28,0:05:47.28,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.28,0:05:49.59,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna be a fun night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.80,0:05:52.98,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, move your cars!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.98,0:05:53.95,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.05,0:06:05.12,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The Redsuns'll manage the\Nrace again.  Is that alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.12,0:06:06.01,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.01,0:06:09.85,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Please assign some people from\Nthe Speedstars as officials.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.85,0:06:10.57,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.57,0:06:12.90,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Iketani, I'll be at the finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.41,0:06:14.42,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,We're counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.86,0:06:21.32,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Keisuke, I'll be at the five\Nsequential hairpins.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.97,0:06:24.18,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryosuke will win, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.18,0:06:26.05,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have our revenge, won't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.05,0:06:27.24,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.24,0:06:30.74,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how fast he is,\Nmy brother won't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.74,0:06:32.11,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I think so, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.11,0:06:33.58,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.32,0:07:02.57,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, this is Fujiwara Tofu...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.57,0:07:04.36,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.36,0:07:08.31,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Bunta, I just got to Akina.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.31,0:07:11.30,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The galleries are packed.\NYou'd be surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.71,0:07:13.89,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.24,0:07:18.33,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think Takumi'll win?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.33,0:07:22.42,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,His opponent is the street king,\Nthe fastest in Gunma.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.42,0:07:24.18,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.18,0:07:26.73,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't have anything else\Nto say, I'm hanging up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.93,0:07:30.27,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Bun...Bunta.\NBunta, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.26,0:07:33.27,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hang up on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.75,0:08:00.01,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.  Report on each corner's condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.67,0:08:02.86,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.  This is the first corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.86,0:08:04.37,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,We're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.21,0:08:10.84,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,This is from the skating rink.\NThe straightaway is clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.13,0:08:17.07,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the No. 17 hairpin.\NWe're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.60,0:08:21.38,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the five sequential hairpins.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.38,0:08:24.27,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no traffic.\NWe're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.63,0:08:30.93,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,This is No. 6.  We're moving the\Ngallery's cars, but it'll be ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.02,0:08:56.55,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The tension's so high,\Nand my throat's dry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.55,0:08:59.22,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart's pounding.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.22,0:09:03.03,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The entire mountain pass\Nis filled with tension.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.03,0:09:04.28,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.28,0:09:06.63,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Takumi'll be alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.49,0:09:12.16,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Takumi, your opponent is one\Nof the best Road Racers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.16,0:09:14.75,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}It's alright to lose,\Nbut drive your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.31,0:09:17.28,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Takumi, good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.28,0:09:20.15,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I believe that you'll win!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.12,0:09:28.58,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}There's no way my brother'll lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.58,0:09:34.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}But when the Eight-Six races, unexpected\Nthings happen on Mt. Akina...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:09:57.46,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, but what about the battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.46,0:09:59.38,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It hasn't started yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.38,0:10:01.60,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.  Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.67,0:10:10.73,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the starting point.\NHow's the finish line?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.54,0:10:14.88,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's ready.\NBegin any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.52,0:10:21.28,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's start.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.28,0:10:22.38,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.66,0:10:27.37,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me count it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.37,0:10:30.15,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to do it for this\Nparticular race.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.15,0:10:30.91,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.26,0:10:40.42,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I won't let anybody else do it for the race\Nbetween my brother and the Eight-Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.53,0:10:43.98,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna count down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.43,0:11:28.51,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Five...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.51,0:11:29.55,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...four...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.55,0:11:30.55,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...three...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.55,0:11:31.55,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...two...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.55,0:11:32.55,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.55,0:11:33.60,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.77,0:11:46.62,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Takumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.77,0:11:46.62,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}Go, Takumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.32,0:11:55.71,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Good, good!\NThe start was even!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.50,0:12:03.58,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Takumi's taken the lead!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.58,0:12:05.89,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi, go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.68,0:12:13.78,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}That's my brother's style.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.78,0:12:15.50,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}For an important race...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.50,0:12:18.45,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}...he lets his opponent go ahead and\Nthen passes him at the critical point.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.45,0:12:24.26,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}He's won that way before, and there's no\Nerror in his logic for the fastest driving.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.89,0:13:08.50,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Both are incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.50,0:13:10.37,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What a tight twin drift!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.32,0:13:17.17,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi Ryosuke usually\Ndoesn't use drift that hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.67,0:13:20.41,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Both are showing off from the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.75,0:13:35.28,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}It's drift versus drift!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.28,0:13:38.44,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}Even Takahashi Ryosuke is using\Ndrift from the very start.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.93,0:13:42.51,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He must be trying to win with\NTakumi's specialty...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.51,0:13:45.35,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...to keep his status as the street king.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.06,0:13:49.91,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}Takumi's doing great, it's\Ngonna be a great battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.08,0:13:54.03,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi, please win, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.03,0:13:55.37,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Iketani?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.93,0:13:58.83,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.29,0:14:05.73,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I'm surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.73,0:14:08.52,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}The Eight-Six's motion is totally\Ndifferent from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.70,0:14:38.13,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}As I thought, he's improved.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.64,0:14:49.15,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}He doesn't countersteer at the end\Nof his drift like before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.15,0:14:53.73,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}But the angle of the countersteer\Nright after the turn-in is also smaller.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.13,0:14:57.76,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I don't understand.  How did\Nhe eliminate that weakness?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.39,0:15:05.24,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}He hasn't raced very many times, but he's\Nimproved, one race after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.97,0:15:09.91,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I'll have to change my simulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.51,0:15:15.27,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}But that's all, and the result\Nwill be the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.27,0:15:18.40,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}My theory for the fastest\Ndriving is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.46,0:15:25.75,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me make this clear, Takeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.75,0:15:30.18,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't park here because\NI saw your car.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.18,0:15:32.86,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,So don't get the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.80,0:15:39.26,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided to come here\Nbeforehand, so get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.26,0:15:40.55,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.55,0:15:44.23,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided to watch the race from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.73,0:15:46.73,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't YOU get lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.02,0:15:53.78,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the amateurs in the galleries\Nchose famous places...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.78,0:15:56.19,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...like the five sequential hairpins.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.19,0:16:00.49,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, but they can't settle\Nthe match there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.49,0:16:03.74,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the only place\Nthey can make a go at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.74,0:16:06.18,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You thought so, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.18,0:16:08.00,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to say it's just what\NI'd expect from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.00,0:16:10.18,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Same to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.58,0:16:15.89,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, there's only\Nus two around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.89,0:16:21.40,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who don't know us might think\Nthat we're close friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.73,0:16:24.98,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.73,0:16:24.98,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}Disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.90,0:16:36.74,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Here they come...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.62,0:16:57.81,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Both cars are so close\Nto the guardrail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.40,0:17:09.06,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible.\NIt's so shocking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.06,0:17:12.86,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,No time to waste.\NI'd better call him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.27,0:17:19.12,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.78,0:17:22.54,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Fujiwara...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.54,0:17:24.95,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}Hey, Bunta, can you hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.95,0:17:26.67,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Not you again...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.67,0:17:28.66,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}Hey, listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.96,0:17:31.78,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,They just passed in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.78,0:17:35.13,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Both cars passed by while\Ndrifting really hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.13,0:17:37.63,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi's Eight-Six has taken the lead...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.63,0:17:40.96,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}...and the FC is right on his tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.68,0:17:44.93,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi's in front?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.93,0:17:46.56,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That's bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.27,0:17:49.06,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.06,0:17:50.48,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.48,0:17:53.71,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Think about it, Yuichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.71,0:17:57.93,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The chaser has an advantage over\Nthe one who's driving in front.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.93,0:17:58.95,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just common sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.30,0:18:01.91,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.63,0:18:09.88,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The one chasing can closely watch the line\Nand rhythm taken by his opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.88,0:18:12.70,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who're skilled enough can\Ncopy that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.70,0:18:15.86,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}But if he can pull away...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.13,0:18:20.47,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The one driving in front\Nfeels a lot of pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.26,0:18:40.18,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If your opponent follows you at the same\Nspeed, you feel mentally cornered.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.31,0:18:45.31,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't pull away while\Nyou're driving your best...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.31,0:18:48.75,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...you start wondering if the opponent is\Nfar more skilled than expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.46,0:19:00.78,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially since Takumi has no experience\Nin managing the pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.78,0:19:04.14,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He must be scared by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.64,0:19:06.71,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He is?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.71,0:19:09.95,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll call you once it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.27,0:19:17.66,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Will he lose...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.31,0:19:19.78,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.17,0:20:19.72,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,They're coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.70,0:20:31.61,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,My god!\NI can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.78,0:20:38.94,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}This is corner number 24!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.94,0:20:42.01,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}The Eight-Six and Ryosuke's\NFC have just passed by.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.01,0:20:46.24,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}And I got the split time,\Nand it's incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.24,0:20:47.73,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}If they keep this pace...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.73,0:20:52.43,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}...they'll shorten the Eight-Six's last\Ncourse record by 7 or 8 seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.43,0:20:54.61,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}Anyway, that's my report.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.09,0:21:00.23,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}They're gonna be faster than\Nour race by 7 or 8 seconds?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.23,0:21:01.73,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Gimme a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.73,0:21:06.68,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}So this is what my brother\Nmeant by driving his best.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.68,0:21:08.83,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}It's almost scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.65,0:21:12.61,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Tonight's battle will become legendary.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.33,0:21:16.14,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi's still in front.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.14,0:21:18.48,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!\NHe'll do it, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.48,0:21:22.03,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but I wonder how\Nlong he can hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.34,0:21:25.90,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,His opponent is Takahashi Ryosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.90,0:21:32.21,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If Takumi finishes the race safely,\NI'll be satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.48,0:22:00.04,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}He's staying right on my tail even though\NI'm driving at full throttle.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.67,0:22:04.03,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I can't shake him, no matter\Nhow fast I drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.67,0:22:11.84,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}It's no good, I might lose this battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.27,0:22:14.61,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Takahashi Ryosuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.61,0:22:17.76,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}...he's not a driver someone\Nlike me can defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.54,0:22:20.68,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I don't want to lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.68,0:22:23.25,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}...but I'm losing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.28,0:22:43.94,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Ai ni tsukarehate samayotte ta koro}Being tired of love, I wandered around...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.36,0:22:50.68,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Yokubou dake ni kararete miushinatteita}...I lost myself to carnal desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.88,0:23:05.66,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Kimagure na unmei wa mujaki na hitomi ni miserate yuku}Innocent eyes slowly charm my unpredictable fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.25,0:23:10.62,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Sake bara no youni akaku}Bloom red like a rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.62,0:23:14.09,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Tsuyoku tsuyoku kimo wo daite}Strongly, strongly I hold you tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.09,0:23:21.05,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Tatta hitotsu kono omoi wo shinjitsu da to ieru}I can tell that only this feeling is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.05,0:23:25.92,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Yorokobi wo kanadeyou}Let's play the melody of pleasure...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.92,0:23:30.75,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Kagayaku mirai e}...into the bright future.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.46,0:23:52.86,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Ah Kazoekirenai hodo tashikameaou}Let's make it sure over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.86,0:23:58.07,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Jounetu yo eien e todoke}This passion will be eternal.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.81,0:24:02.04,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Sake bara no youni akaku}Bloom red like a rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.04,0:24:05.58,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Tsuyoku tsuyoku dakishimete}Strongly, strongly I hold you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.58,0:24:12.47,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Tatoe nani wo ushinattemo kono ude wo hanasanai}Even if I lose everything, I won't let your arm go.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.47,0:24:17.35,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Utsukushiku Karen ni sake}Bloom beautifully and gracefully.
