Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.98,0:24:33.67,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I think Takumi'll win, as I expected...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.93,0:24:31.97,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}I don't want to lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.97,0:24:33.27,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}Hello, this is Fujiwara Tofu Shop...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.67,0:24:36.03,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if I'll be able to...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.34,0:24:35.18,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}...with an Eight-Six...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.18,0:24:36.03,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}...his sense of drift...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.03,0:24:36.81,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryousuke, I...!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.29,0:24:39.35,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...Takumi'll definitely win this race!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.35,0:24:41.30,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Takumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.30,0:24:43.06,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.06,0:24:44.30,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi, keep up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.77,0:24:45.65,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Go for the win!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.97,0:24:52.03,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}So many opinions are crossing over,\Nbut the race'll be settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.03,0:24:56.33,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}Next time on Initial D, the last episode:\N"New Downhill Legend!"
