Dialogue: 1,0:24:54.78,0:24:59.94,MainStyle,,0000,0430,0260,,Next Time:
Dialogue: 1,0:24:54.78,0:24:59.94,MainStyle,,0000,0060,0190,,New Downhill Legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.04,0:24:58.55,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't miss it!
